data.description: Welcome home to 8575 Purity Drive. This well taken care of single story ranch style home is a must see! As you walk through the front entryway you'll be blown away by the living space this open floor plan has to offer. The large living room with lots of natural light and brand new vinyl plank flooring opens up to the spacious kitchen.  If you love to cook then this kitchen is made for you. With enough cabinet storage for any kitchen appliance or cookware you could think of. Also plenty of counter space and a central island. Each guest bedroom is very spacious and the large master bedroom has a full walk-in closet. Seller offering one year Elite Plan Home WarrantyHot water heater replaced 2023Flooring in living room and kitchen replaced 2023Full HVAC system replaced in 2017
